Lindelin:
  Barblands:
    - big part of the old wars
      - between the orcs and humans
      - lots of bloody battles
      - human skel3tons

  Kragspeak:
    - Run by the Red Order
    - Originally a shrine or religious monument that became overcrowded.

    - The Mountains:
      - large creatures created the towers
      - queeen controls the hive
      - six legs
      - giant

    - The peaks:
      - No one's been this deep in the peaksss
      - cool trees that no one has ever seen before
      - Thicc dark magical forest
      - High in the mountains
      - We sensed powerful abjuration magic

  Fishca:
    population: seventy something

  Baddabrush Forrest:
    - a massive forrest
    - Massive lake at the centre of the forrest
      - stream coming from the river john

  Thorton:
    - Thriving village at one time
      - main passage from orc land to lindellen
      - origin place of most of the half orc
    - During the great war the town was ravaged
      - everyone evacuated
        - since then rumours that the town is haunted have spread

